			"id":"debee7fda91c53ff",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"## Problems : \n\n1. A single PostgreSQL page is 8 KB and stores tuples (rows). What happens if a single tuple is larger than a page?\n",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":2500,
			"y":-1100,
